div.div: Desynchronization period for Major update. Breaking changes are made to schema or API endpoint design, and it's either impossible, too dangerous, too difficult or too expensive to offer a migration that allows for cross version compatibility upon submission. During this time, api request can fail with a unique Error Code, and we can message folks to instruct them to refresh page, try again later or perform expected recovery steps.
